# Enforce LF line endings for all text files, in the repo and on checkout.
#
# Without this, a Windows checkout (core.autocrlf=true) gives every file CRLF
# line endings, which fails Prettier's format gate (endOfLine defaults to "lf")
# on the developer's machine while passing on Linux/CI — a confusing split.
# Pinning eol=lf makes `npm run format:check` behave identically everywhere.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets: never normalize line endings or attempt to diff them.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.webp binary
*.avif binary
*.ico  binary
*.pdf  binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
